title: given the information [[id:c94b60e6-2c39-451d-af2d-129acbefe2e1][SAS]]
pid: f422fcc9-01db-40c8-a472-d0614af7dfdf
body: |2-
  Solve [[id:75dd2eca-6cb9-417a-807c-dc6ce58f8397][the law of cosines]] for a:
    a = sqrt ( b**2 + c**2 -
               2 * b * c * cos A )
  As Haskell:
    a b a_angle c = sqrt ( b**2 + c**2 - 2 * b * c * cos a_angle )
